#~ "in <filename>$KDEDIR/share/apps/katepart/libraries</filename>. If you "
#~ "want to use them in your script, which is required to use some of the "
#~ "<classname>Document</classname> or <classname>View</classname> functions, "
#~ "please include the needed library by using:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "De API voor scripts hier aanwezig is beschikbaar in alle scripts, bijv. "
#~ "scripts voor inspringen en opdrachtregels. De <classname>Cursor</"
#~ "classname> en <classname>Range</classname> worden geleverd door "
#~ "biblitheekbestanden in <filename>$KDEDIR/share/apps/katepart/libraries</"
#~ "filename>. Als u ze in uw script wilt gebruiken, wat vereist is om "
#~ "bepaalde <classname>Document</classname> of <classname>View</classname> "
